E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1064','268','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，从县创建办传来喜讯：中央文明委在中国文明网对拟表彰的第三批全国文明城市（区）、文明村镇、文明单位的公示中，嘉鱼县城入选全国文明村镇候选名录，田野集团股份有限公司（本部）入选全国文明单位候选名录。嘉鱼是此次评选中咸宁市唯一入选的县城。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">近年来，我县加大投入，基础设施建设不断得到完善，大街小巷秩序得到明显改善，市政基础设施、公共交通、医疗卫生、公共绿地等重点区域和关键环节达标水平明显提升。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">从</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2004</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年至今，<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">嘉鱼</span>县的城市建设一步一个脚印，先后完成了从一个小城到省级<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">文明</span>县城、省级卫生县城再到省级园林城市的完美跨越，目前正向全国<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">文明</span>县城挺进。上个月，我县官桥村顺利通过中国生态文化协会的评选验收，被授予第二批&ldquo;全国生态文化村&rdquo;，这是此次评选中，我省唯一获此殊荣的村庄。</span><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> </font></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">相关链接：</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><a href=\\\\\"http://www.wenming.cn/wmcj_pd/index_5857.shtml\\\\\"><u><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; color: red; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">中央文明委关于第三批全国文明城市（区）、文明村镇、文明单位候选名单的公示</span></span></u><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"color: red; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></a></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1065','268','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/chuangjianwenmingweishengchengshi/2011-12-09/bbc769cc545285246ae6570adaa84562.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">饶自斌正在查看路边建筑垃圾<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">11</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>日上午，副县长饶自斌带领县创建办、住建局、城管局负责人前往东岳路、北门湖，冒雨检查环境卫生整治情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在东岳路，当看到街道两边地面干净、环境卫生明显改善，占道经营现象大为减少时，饶自斌对前段时间做的工作表示认可，对部分地方的积水和堆放的建筑垃圾要求包保单位处理好。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在北门湖，当看到菜场附近占道经营、乱摆卖、乱堆放、垃圾乱扔等现象依然存在，特别是一些沿街商铺&ldquo;门前四包&rdquo;责任落实不到位、垃圾清扫不及时、路面污迹明显等现象，饶自斌当即要求包保单位必须限时整改好。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">饶自斌说，做好城市管理迎检工作是县委县政府进一步改善民生，检验干部执政能力，推动嘉鱼发展的重要举措，是为了进一步巩固省级文明卫生县城创建成果，为创建国家级文明县城打好基础。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">饶自斌要求，东岳路、北门湖包保单位负责人要抓紧抓好路面硬化、修复工程，道路两边要绿化，无裸露地段；垃圾要及时清扫清运，各类垃圾设施要完好无损，垃圾箱每<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>米摆放一个；下水道排水要畅通，路面及边沟无积水。总体做到六无，即无乱停乱靠、无游商游贩、无占道经营、无乱搭乱建、无乱牵乱挂、无&ldquo;牛皮癣&rdquo;。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n</div>');");
