i-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏朝东指出，深入开展&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;，有利于转变干部作风、提升服务效能、改善发展环境，促使党员干部振奋精神、真抓实干、勇于担当、创先争优，真正做到治庸提能力、治懒增效率、治散正风气、治软鼓干劲。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏朝东强调，委局机关党员干部要认真学习&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;相关文件精神和实施方案，着力打造&ldquo;两个满意&rdquo;，即让干部满意、让群众满意；做到&ldquo;三个结合&rdquo;，即与&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动相结合、与&ldquo;两违&rdquo;防控相结合、与项目建设相结合；解决&ldquo;四个问题&rdquo;，即四庸、四懒、四散、四软问题；提高&ldquo;五个意识&rdquo;，即能力意识、危机意识、责任意识、服务意识、席位意识。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">他要求广大纪检监察干部要从自身抓起，做好&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;的先锋和表率，并充分发挥纪检监察机关的职能作用，改进干部作风，把治庸问责各项工作落到实处，推进全县治庸问责工作顺利开展，确保让干部满意、让群众满意。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县监察局局长周长明主持动员会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县纪委监察局机关及派出（驻）纪检组监察室全体党员干部参加会议。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 150%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; word-break: break-all; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></span></font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<o:p></o:p>');");
