视治庸问责对推进宣传、思想工作的重要作用，清醒认识部机关存在的问题，切实加强组织领导，认真抓好落实，力求让治庸问责发挥提神、提速、提劲的积极效果。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">刘合权强调，针对庸懒散软现象，要做到敢治敢问、严治严问、善治善问、常治常问，以抓学习治庸、抓作风治懒、抓纪律治散、抓管理治软，不断提高机关干部执行力，始终保持良好的精神状态，有力推动宣传工作上新台阶。同时，还要充分发挥宣传部门的职能作用，做好宣传舆论引导，推动全县治庸问责行动取得实效。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议传达了全县治庸问责动员大会、全县违法用地违规建设整治动员大会、全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会精神，并对县委宣传部在马鞍山村开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动作了具体工作部署。</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></span></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1079','284','吴超','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，全县治庸问责工作动员大会召开后，县检察院党组高度重视，当天下午便召开专题会议，</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">学习传达会议精神，研究制定了五项措施全力推进治庸问责工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一是成立工作专班。迅速成立以党组书记、检察长邓佛围为组长的领导小组，领导小组下设办公室，抽调</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">名干警，负责开展治庸问责日常工作。二是制定实施方案。结合检察工作实际制定实施方案，明确宣传发动、自查整改、督察问责、总结提高等阶段的工作任务和要求，确保治庸问责工作有序推进。三是狠抓宣传发动。召开党组会、中心组学习扩大会，统一领导班子、中层干部思想认识。认真开好全体干警动员大会，切实把治庸问责要求贯彻到每一名干警。四是推行开门问责。开辟网站专栏，设置举报箱，公布举报电话，畅通外部监督渠道，积极接受群众对检察院治庸问责工作的监督。五是实行边查边改。针对考勤制度中存在的问题，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日便立即整改。进一步完善车辆管理制度、请销假等制度，加大检务督察力度，力促治庸问责工作取得实效。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1080','284','鲁攻玉','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，按照县委的统一要求，县人大机关召开治庸问责暨&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作动员大会，对人大机关治庸问责工作和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作进行动员和部署。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在组织全体机关干部集中学习治庸问责及&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作有关文件和全县动员大会领导讲话精神后，县人大常委会主任李鹏谋对人大机关推进治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作明确提出了四点要求。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一是不唱空调，真正在思想认识上抓落实。治庸问责工作是当前全县上下组织开展的一项集中整治活动，也是加快建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的一次具体现实行动，人大机关全体干部要在思想上高度重视，认识上高度统一，步调上高度一致，努力在治庸问责中改进机关作风，创新工作机制，加强队伍建设，提高干部素质，圆满完成&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作任务，以实际行动为农民群众办实事。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">二是不讲条件，真正在履行职责上抓落实。县人大常委会的工作职责主要就是依法监督、依法决定重大事项。在实际工作中，人大机关全体干部要始终坚持党的领导，坚持寓监督于支持之中，牢固树立&ldquo;不是中心要始终围绕中心，不在一线要始终关注一线&rdquo;观念，对县委决策部署的治庸问责活动以及筹资修路、筹资挖塘等中心工作，人大机关不仅要不讲条件、率先落实，还要履职尽责，加强视察检查督促，真正办成群众满意工程。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">三是不打乱仗，真正在组织实施上抓落实。对于县委统一安排部署的治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动等近期中心工作，办公室要切实制定工作方案，组建工作专班，明确工作职责，认真组织好实施好，不打乱仗。治庸问责工作由人大机关党总支具体负责，突出抓好宣传动员、学习教育、自查反省、深入整改、责任追究、建章立制等重点环节，真正把问题找准、把原因查清，把思想摆正，把体制理顺。&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动由专班人员具体负责，机关干部全员参与，重点是广泛宣传政策，积极出谋划策，帮助联点村完成好改造当家塘、疏通主沟渠等农田水利基本建设任务，增强抗灾减灾能力。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">四是不走过场，真正在增强实效上抓落实。人大机关要以深入开展治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动为契机，进一步加强机关自身建设，健全完善机关各项工作制度、人大代表工作制度以及主任会议、人大常委会议、人民代表大会议事规则，进一步深入基层调查研究，为群众办实事解难事，密切党群干群关系，让组织放心，让群众满意。<br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1081','284','财政宣','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日下午，县财政局组织全体工作人员，召开了治庸问责工作动员大会。会议传达和学习了县委书记熊征宇关于治庸问责的讲话和县治庸问责工作方案，下发了《嘉鱼县财政局开展治庸问责工作实施方案》，县政协副主席、县财政局局长刘平作了动员讲话，部署安排了该局治庸问责工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">刘平在动员讲话中要求，全体财政干部职工要以对党、对人民群众、对财政事业、对自己高度负责的态度，治庸提能力，治懒增效率，治散正风气，触及痛处找问题，对症下药建制度，敢于问责抓追究，集中精力解决干部队伍中工作松懈、纪律松散等&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;现象。各单位主要负责人要在局党组的领导下，切实履行好对此项工作的领导职责，按照局党组的部署，宣传好、组织好、开展好此项活动。局治庸问责工作领导小组办公室要切实履行工作职责，坚持严肃处理、决不姑息的工作原则，加强对此项工作的督查力度。要建立治庸问责长效机制，加强制度建设和落实力度，做到思想认识到位，查找问题到位，原因分析到位，明确方向到位，落实整改到位，深入推进责任财政、廉洁财政、高效财政建设，确保财政工作作风明显进步，服务效能明显提升，充分发挥财政部门在进一步优化全县发展环境、推进嘉鱼科学发展、跨越发展中的职能作用。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1082','284','张旭','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日上午，县委办公室召开治庸问责动员大会，学习传达全县治庸问责工作动员会议精神，安排部署县委办公室&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会上，县委办公室主任章斌指出，治庸问责是建设湖北经济强县，长江临港新城的需要；是提高机关工作效率，树立机关形象的需要；是强化干部建设，修身养性的需要。县委办公室作为县级党政机关办公室的龙头和引擎，要以身作则，第一时间采取行动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">章斌强调，县委办公室&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;工作的开展，要领会精神，强化认识；把握环节，扎实推进；加强领导，抓出成效；结合自身实际把&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;落到实处，切实把县委办公室各项工作抓实、抓好。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县委办公室副主任郑德朝主持动员会。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县委办公室</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">全体机关干部参加会议。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1083','284','县教育局','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">全县治庸问责工作动员大会召开后，县教育局迅速行动，第一时间启动了全县教育系统治庸问责工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，教育局党组召开专题会议，传达全县治庸问责工作动员大会精神，研究全县教育系统治庸问责工作。同时，成立领导小组和工作专班，出台了《县教育局关于扎实开展治庸问责工作的实施方案》。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，召开了嘉鱼县教育局治庸问责工作动员大会，教育局领导班子成员、机关及二级单位全体干部、县直学校全体班子成员、乡镇中学（中心学校）校长参加了动员大会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县教育局党组书记、局长高汉阳做了动员报告。高汉阳强调，全县教育系统广大党员干部要统一思想，充分认识开展治庸问责工作的重大意义。要突出抓好&ldquo;宣传发动、自查整改、督查问责、总结提高&rdquo;四个环节，采取有效措施，将治庸问责工作进行到底，着力解决&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;等方面的突出问题，形成&ldquo;精神面貌大改观、干部作风大转变、服务效能大提升、教育质量大提高&rdquo;的良好局面，为建设教育质量强县、办好人民满意教育做出新贡献。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">高汉阳要求，全县教育系统在治庸问责工作上要做到&ldquo;三抓三强化&rdquo;。&ldquo;三抓&rdquo;是：抓教育，提振精神；抓问责，敢于碰硬；抓机制，实现长效。&ldquo;三强化&rdquo;是：强化组织领导，强化工作责任，强化督办检查。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">教育局动员大会后，教育局机关、二级单位、县直学校的治庸问责工作已经轰轰烈烈地全面展开。教育局还以嘉鱼教育网为平台，开设了&ldquo;治庸问责在行动&rdquo;专栏，全面宣传教育系统治庸问责工作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1084','284','张姝、司法宣','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日上午，县司法局召开治庸问责工作动员大会。局机关及各镇司法所全体干部参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，县司法局局长章少阶强调全体干部要认真学习&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;相关文件精神和实施方案，恪尽职守、尽职尽责；针对存在的&ldquo;庸懒散软&rdquo;问题，提出了&ldquo;四认真<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>，即认真对待、认真查找、认真整改、认真督查；要求从考勤、会风抓起，对出现的问题进行通报上墙，全局干部进行交叉督促、相互监督，确保治庸工作的有效开展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">大会还传达了全县治庸问责动员大会、全县违法用地违规建设整治动员大会、全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会精神，并对开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动作了具体工作部署。据悉，该局专门成立了治庸问责工作领导小组，制订了切实可行的实施方案，以强化全局干部的责任意识、服务意识和奋发有为意识，促进全局上下形成求真务实、干事创业的良好环境和氛围。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1085','284','鲁辉','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日下午，潘家湾镇召开治庸问责工作动员大会，安排部署治庸问责工作及当前各项工作。县委副书记李国光，人大副主任戴书萍出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">李国光表示，潘家湾镇具有良好的发展基础和精神动力，是全省综合实力百强乡镇，也是全省八十八个城镇建设重点乡镇之一，受到省市县高度重视。全镇要进一步明确方向，谋划发展，抢抓武汉新港、临港新城、咸嘉新城、武深高速等一大批项目建设机遇，努力实现临港经济重镇、全县经济副中心的奋斗目标。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">李国光指出，精神懈怠是最大的危险，要不断提高认识，坚定信心，切实抓好治庸问责工作，彻底转变工作作风，促进镇域经济持续发展。他强调，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组要切实帮助所驻点的村，认真开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，把活动的开展与治庸问责工作紧密结合起来。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会议安排部署了全镇治庸问责工作、&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作和冬季计划生育突击月工作；宣读了《调整全镇农田水利工程建设指挥部成员的通知》和《关于下达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年度水利建设计划任务的通知》。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，潘家湾镇党委书记周亚澜就如何抓好治庸问责工作作了表态发言，他指出，目前该镇机关和窗口单位确实存在一些庸、懒、散、软的现象，开展治庸问责工作既是政治要求，也是政治任务，也是潘湾发展的必然要求，要坚持从学习、查找差距、评议整改、长效管理、结合工作几个方面抓好治庸问责工作，严明纪律，对暴露出来的问题绝不姑息、严惩不贷，从而不断促进思想、作风、业绩的转变。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动驻潘湾工作队成员，该镇全体机关干部，各村书记、计生专干，镇直部门负责人参加了会议。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1086','284','蔡雪峰','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>日上午，官桥镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动、&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治、治庸问责活动动员及党报党刊征订工作大会在该镇五楼会议室召开。县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队全体成员，全体机关干部，镇直各部门负责人，各村（社区）党组织书记、村主任共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">110</span>余人参加了会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会议由官桥镇党委副书记、镇长朱明凤主持。该镇党委、政府分管纪检、城建、组织、宣传工作的领导分别传达了相关会议精神，领学了镇党委、政府相关文件，部分镇直部门、村负责人就相关工作作了表态发言。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">该镇党委书记杨富佳就上述各项工作进行了动员部署与强调，县驻官桥镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队队长、县纪委常委、监察局副局长孙强参加了会议并就&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动提了要求。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1087','284','新宣办','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2011/1204/20111204024802718.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">图为治庸工作动员会现场</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>日上午，新街镇隆重召开治庸问责工作动员大会，传达市、县关于推进治庸问责工作的实施方案精神，对治庸问责等工作进行动员部署。县政协主席葛婷，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">葛婷说，开展治庸问责工作，是全县当前的一项重要任务，是贯彻落实胡锦涛总书记&ldquo;七一&rdquo;重要讲话精神，有效防范精神懈怠的危险、能力不足的危险、脱离群众的危险的现实需要；是推动嘉鱼全面建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的迫切要求；是转变干部作风、密切干群关系的重要途径。她强调，新街镇党员干部务必站在政治和全局的高度，深刻认识这次开展治庸问责工作的重要意义，充分利用新街在区位、交通、资源、人才等方面的优势，切实增强危机意识、城建意识、中心意识、担当意识、团结意识，以不断提高机关行政效能，不断优化经济发展环境，推动新街经济社会跨越发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">刘合权指出，全体党员干部要用真查实改的精神开展好治庸问责工作，要以敢治敢问的态度，善治善问的方法，常治常问的机制，&ldquo;问&rdquo;出执行力、创造力和凝聚力；要用真情实感的态度抓好&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，充分尊重群众意愿，因地制宜开展工作，县直部门驻村工作队要尽力尽量而为，努力为群众办好事办实事；要用真抓实干的作风推进全镇各项工作，要学会&ldquo;弹钢琴&rdquo;，科学摆布工作关系，把治庸问责、&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动及水利建设等工作结合起来，确保经济建设、社会发展、计划生育等各项工作圆满完成年度目标。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该镇党委书记杨新武说，这次治庸问责工作一个重要特点就是以问题为导向，全镇广大党员干部一定要深刻认识&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;对工作的危害，以更高的标准，更强的能力，更硬的作风，更好地适应治庸问责工作的新要求。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"left\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0; mso-pagination: widow-orphan\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动驻新街镇工作队成员，新街镇全体机关干部，各村书记，镇直部门负责人参加了会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1088','284','邱蓓','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日上午，嘉鱼县农业局召开了动员大会，及时传达学习、贯彻落实县委、县政府关于在全县开展治庸问责工作的精神，动员安排全局治庸问责工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">动员会上，该局局长邓卫东强调全县农业系统治庸问责工作要突出&ldquo;五查五看&rdquo;，即一查思想观念，看思想观念是否适应时代发展要求，有无墨守陈规、因循守旧及在体制机制上制约科学发展、跨越式发展的突出问题；二查工作业绩，看本职工作是否创先争优，看业务工作是否有进步，是否存在工作业绩平淡，不作为等问题；三查日常管理，看日常管理是否严格；四查工作作风，看党员干部是否存在精神懈怠、萎靡不振、敷衍塞责、推诿扯皮，只求过得去、不求过得硬、<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>当一天和尚撞一天钟<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>等问题；五查制度纪律，看各项规章制度是否健全，党员干部是否严守纪律，有无违反人事、财经及项目管理规定的问题。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"> <o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-spacerun: yes\\\\\">&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">同时要做到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>六个严禁<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>，即严禁无关人员进入办公场所，严禁无故迟到早退，严禁在办公场所进餐或吃零食，严禁上网炒股、打牌、下棋、玩游戏，严禁串门闲聊、嬉闹，严禁办理其它与工作无关的事项。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1089','284','张旭','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2011/1205/20111205044624488.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日，县人民政府办公室召开治庸问责工作动员大会，学习传达全县治庸问责工作动员会议精神，安排部署县政府办治庸问责工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县政府办主任余忠东指出，治庸问责是加强党风廉政建设的需要，是建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的需要，是加强办公室自身建设的需要；全体机关干部在思想上要高度统一认识，行动措施要迅速到位，能力绩效要迅速提高。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会上，余忠东传达了全县治庸问责动员大会、全县违法用地违规建设整治动员大会、全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会精神，并就全县重点项目建设政府办项目督办工作作了具体安排部署。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会议宣读了《县人民政府办公室关于成立治庸问责工作领导小组的通知》及《县人民政府办公室关于印发县政府办扎实开展治庸问责工作实施方案的通知》，实施方案从指导思想、方法步骤、工作要求三方面具体安排部署了县政府办治庸问责工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">县政府办全体机关干部参加了会议。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; word-break: break-all; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1090','284','龙光辉','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日</st1:chsdate>，县林业局举办干部业务学习活动，人人上台讲课，人人对治庸问责作表态承诺，动真格，下重手，全面推进林业系统治庸问责活动深入开展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在治庸问责活动中，县林业局将采取&ldquo;四个结合&rdquo;的办法扎实开展治庸问责工作。将治庸问责与日常管理相结合，抓工作纪律，严格实行工作考勤、考核、奖惩等制度，切实提高干部职工履职能力；将治庸问责与业务工作相结合，抓好当前的林业开发、森林防火等林业重点工作，重点整治工作中没有工作激情，精神状态差，不讲效率，工作被动应付，不履行职责，办事超出规定时限或承诺时限的现象；将治庸问责与队伍培训建设相结合，抓学习培训，着力打造一支业务精良的队伍；将治庸问责与单位效能建设相结合，抓好文明单位创建，实行首问负责制、限时办结制、服务承诺制等制度，规范行政行为，不断提升群众、企业对林业服务的满意度，推进全县林业跨越式发展。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1091','284','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2011-12-09/fc5441d834089cc4f71d117a9943de4e.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，高铁岭镇召开治庸问责暨&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会，学习传达县委县政府相关会议精神，并部署全镇治庸问责及&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作安排。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该镇党委书记张行泽指出，在开展治庸问责工作中，要<span style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">树立责任意识，着力解决工作态度、劳动纪律问题；</span>树立勤政意识，着力解决&ldquo;不作为、慢作为、乱作为&rdquo;问题；树立效率意识，着力解决&ldquo;程序不优、能力不强、执行不力&rdquo;问题；树立服务意识，着力解决&ldquo;门难进、脸难看、话难听、事难办&rdquo;问题。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">张行泽指出，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动驻村工作组要与各村紧密联系，指导各村对塘堰整治科学规划，合理布局；镇村要积极与工作组对接，积极谋划，主动配合，着重解决与群众关系最密切的突出问题；要积极整合资金、统筹推进，努力建成一批促发展、惠民生的项目。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该镇党委副书记、镇长刘珈对治庸问责、三万活动等当前各项重点工作进行了安排部署。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\\\\\">据悉，高铁岭镇在治庸问责工作中坚持把思想教育、检查整改、树立典型、责任追究、完善机制贯穿始终，突出抓好宣传发动、自查整改、督查问责、总结提高四个环节，采取集中检查、明查暗访、公开承诺、媒体曝光等方式，着力解决机关干部工作中存在的突出问题以及党员干部队伍中存在的能力平庸、业绩平庸，思想懒惰、工作懒惰，纪律作风松散、班子软弱涣散等&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;方面的突出问题。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1092','284','黄念','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日晚<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>点半</st1:chsdate>，渡普镇会议室灯火通明，原来全镇机关干部正认真学习县委关于治庸问责工作会议精神。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">该镇党委书记余洪煌在学习会上指出，全镇机关干部要深刻认识治庸问责的重要性，高度统一思想，在全镇迅速掀起治庸问责大风暴，不断优化全镇发展；要严格按照县委要求，确保治庸问责工作措施到位，强力推进；要健全机制，敢于创新、敢于问责、善于问责，健全监管机制，真正达到治庸问责工作实效。要把治庸问责与日常工作紧密结合，特别是与此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动相结合，为全镇的发展提供强有力的组织保证和作风保障。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">通过学习，镇机关干部纷纷表示获益匪浅，领悟深刻。老干部决心再现当年青春风采，年轻干部表示将以治庸问责为契机督促鼓励自己多学习、多为民服务，为全镇发展努力贡献自己的力量。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1093','284','陈波波','嘉鱼政务网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"IMG_5405_副本.jpg\\\\\" width=\\\\\"500\\\\\" height=\\\\\"375\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2011-12-09/4ad373c1a7cc2c9c0951d8a23916b9e9.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">会议现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">12</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">下午，县水产局召开&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;工作动员会，全面深入的传达了全县治庸问责动员大会的精神，并就治庸问责工作的具体安排做了部署。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: black; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">水产局局长熊仕秀同志要求全局上下要认真领会县委县政府&ldquo;治庸问责&rdquo;动员大会的精神，自查自省，全面清理在工作中所表现出来的&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;等问题，提高工作效率，提升为民服务的意识，端正工作态度，使治庸工作的效果落到实处。结合水产局的具体情况，要突出做到以下四点：在治&ldquo;庸&rdquo;的方面，要杜绝&ldquo;不求有功但求无过&rdquo;的思想，鼓励勇于创新，大胆作为；在治&ldquo;懒&rdquo;方面，要反对&ldquo;做一天和尚撞一天钟&rdquo;的思想，鼓励与时俱进，勤奋学习，努力提升自身的业务水平，为水产事业的发展贡献力量；在治&ldquo;散&rdquo;方面，要强化人员的纪律意识，严禁出现迟到早退，无故旷工，开会不到晚到等散慢行为；在治&ldquo;软&rdquo;方面，要强化干部员工的责任意识，服务意识，出现问题及时解决，不推诿，不懈怠。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1094','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-09/83e0f3a8691128851eb64fce16c698c8.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">座谈会现场</span></div>\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，市综合治理检查组一行来到嘉鱼，对我县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年综治维稳信访工作进行检查考评。县委副书记李国光，县委常委、政法委书记朱从钦，县政协副主席严嘉芬陪同检查。</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">检查组一行到县综治办、维稳办、信访局等部门，以及乡镇、社区进行走访调查，查阅了有关文件、资料、台帐，听取了我县关于</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度综治维稳信访工作的汇报。</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，今年来，我县综治工作突出落实领导责任、基层基础建设、创新社会管理、社会矛盾化解、&ldquo;严打&rdquo;整治和专项斗争、社会治安防控体系建设，以及综治委六部门专项工作，着力构建大综治的工作格局，全县社会保持总体稳定，呈现出&ldquo;八无、一上升&rdquo;的良好态势，即无影响全省的网络舆论事件；无集体赴省进京非访；无影响全县社会稳定的群体性事件；无有影响的重大刑事案件；无恐怖事件发生；无群死群伤灾害事故；无敏感时期、重大活动的安全保卫事故；无在全省造成恶劣影响的政法干警犯罪案件。&ldquo;一上升&rdquo;即公众安全感上升，人民安居乐业。</span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n</span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1095','285','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/e71696a21158701a3ae07a6ea81e41cc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">30</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，嘉鱼召开全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动暨农田水利基本建设动员大会，传达贯彻中央、省、市有关水利工作会议精神，表彰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全县水利建设先进单位，安排部署全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动暨农田水利基本建设工作。省国防科工办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动驻嘉鱼工作组组长周峰，县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂等县四大家领导出席会议。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇在会上作重要讲话，他指出，新一轮&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动和农田水利建设，是加强农业基础设施建设的迫切需要，是抢抓当前水利建设重大政策机遇的迫切需要，全县上下务必高度重视，把抓好&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动各项工作作为当前重中之重的任务。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇强调，在新一轮&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动中，要努力实现&ldquo;三个全覆盖&rdquo;的目标，即所有单位和全体干部都要参与到活动中来，要覆盖所有行政村，覆盖所有农户；要努力实现党员干部作风大转变的目标，以饱满的热情、良好的精神状态、深厚的群众感情，投入到&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动和农田水利建设中去，切实增强与人民群众的血肉联系，团结、依靠和带领广大干部群众加快农田水利建设；要努力实现群众得实惠的目标，根据各地实际需要，开展小型泵站维修、沟渠整修或兴修小水井、小水窖等，力争在全县每个村民小组整治一口当家塘堰。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇要求，全县水利事业迎来了发展的春天，务必要抢抓机遇，理清思路，科学规划，积极争取政策、项目和资金支持；今冬明春的水利建设关系到农业增效，农民增收，务必要抓紧抓实，确保各项工作目标落到实处；要着力解决钱从哪里来、重点抓什么、机制怎么改的问题，精心组织、抢抓时间，迅速进村入户，并拿出工作方案。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂主持会议。他要求各地、各部门要深入宣传，迅速传达贯彻会议精神；要把握重点，迅速掀起水利建设高潮；要迅速行动，加强督办，奋力夺取新一轮&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的新胜利。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东宣读了《</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动实施方案》和《关于表彰</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全县水利建设先进单位的通报》。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">副县长魏萍传达了中央、省、市有关水利工作会议精神，安排部署了全县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度农田水利基本建设工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，县水利局、财政局、国土局和洲湾镇分别作了表态发言；对洲湾镇等</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2011</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年度全县水利建设先进单位进行了颁奖。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1096','285','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/4eb462a59662232e6001a3ab25d1e837.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">在中堡村了解情况</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;我们这次来就是要为老百姓做点实实在在的事。&rdquo;</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，县委常委、县人武部政委杨长江，县委办主任章斌率县委&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队来到洲湾镇花口村和中堡村，在全县率先开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">花口村和中堡村是县委工作队挂点村，昨天全县召开三万活动动员会后，县委工作队迅速行动，组织队员于今天早上就来到村里，与村干部座谈，了解情况。并到村里各个急需修缮的沟渠、塘堰进行了实地查看，制定活动方案，为开展好此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，帮助该村搞好水利设施建设工程做好各项准备工作。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在花口村二组，长达</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">4000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多米的雨水排水沟多年淤积，失去排水功能，导致</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">230</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">户村民面临一下雨家中就渍水的困难。中堡村魏家码泵站由于出水沟太窄无法使用，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多亩农田灌溉缺水。&ldquo;我们不摆花架子，就是要解决这些村民最迫切需要解决的问题。&rdquo;了解到这些该情况后，杨长江表示，工作队将根据实际情况，迅速成立方案，组织机器、人员等，帮助村民疏通渠道、改建泵站，切实为村民解决实际困难。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1097','285','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<p style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/768b8df07940f52db0a6af011332d0d7.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">魏朝东一行实地调研官桥村塘堰建设情况</span>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"1\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东率领纪委监察局领导班子成员深入到官桥镇官桥村，扎实开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">在实地调研了官桥村部分塘堰建设进展，认真听取了该村相关情况介绍后，魏朝东指出，官桥村地域广阔、资源丰富、交通便利。因此镇村干部要以&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动为载体，以&ldquo;挖塘堰、强基础、惠民生&rdquo;为主题，带动其他塘堰及小型水利设施的整治和建设。要进一步拓宽发展思路，壮大村级集体经济，着力解决群众反映强烈的突出问题，切实为村民办实事、办好事，帮助农民增收致富。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">调研期间，县纪委现场为官桥村捐赠三万元现金，用于该村塘堰及小型水利设施的修复建设，并动员各级、各相关部门积极筹资筹劳，投入人力物力财力，支持该村小型水利基础设施的整治和建设。</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，全县&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动动员会召开后，县纪委监察局按照县委县政府的统一部署和要求，迅速行动起来，主动把&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动与新农村建设、治庸问责等工作结合起来，抽调纪检监察机关精兵强将组成驻村工作组，深入农村和农户家中，仔细调查社情民意，准确掌握群众所思、所忧、所盼，扎实开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。</span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/d4d693a6100a238539d8070a99a077cc.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 18px\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">县纪委监察局为官桥村捐款现场</font></span></o:p></span></div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1098','285','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/3997d11a37c3611880359a655fb3fd8e.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">劳动现场<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日，在嘉鱼县州湾镇广福庵村三组，县水利局干部职工与当地村民一起拿起铁锹、上筐清淤泥，疏通沟渠。&ldquo;这条沟已经被淤泥堵塞了，完全通不了水，为了贯彻县委县政府开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的精神，水利局组织<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">50</span>多名干部职工来这里和当地的村民一起疏挖这条沟渠，为附近的耕地提供灌溉保障。&rdquo;县水利局局长夏毅一边挖土，一边对记者说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">该局还现场为广福庵村捐赠三万元现金，用于该村塘堰及小型水利设施的修复建设。&ldquo;我们将把这批资金真正用到水利建设上来，用到实处。将根据各组的实际情况制定开挖沟渠的方案，抢晴天，争雨天，加紧施工，改变我村水利设施滞后的现状&rdquo;。广福庵村党支部书记耿显潮说。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据悉，全县&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动动员会召开后，县水利局按照县委县政府的统一部署和要求，迅速行动起来，成立工作专班，制定实施方案，进村入户，调查摸底，准确掌握群众所思、所忧、所盼，扎实开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1099','285','耿海军','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/ff97978c0127d43ff8b640d5f6debfd3.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">张海河一行实地查看急需整修的塘堰</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: left\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，县委组织部副部长、县公务员局局长张海河带领该局班子成员和驻村工作组深入陆溪镇邱湾村，摸查塘堰沟渠隐患，商讨整治方案，并现场捐赠了三万元资金，以实际行动践行县委县政府&ldquo;挖塘堰、强基础、惠民生&rdquo;的活动。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">公务员局班子成员来到邱湾村后，立即召开村干部座谈会，传达县委县政府开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动精神，宣传党的强农惠农政策，听取该村农田水利设施的情况介绍。随后，公务员局一行在村干部陪同下实地查看了急需整修的塘堰和沟渠，商讨了整治塘堰和沟渠的计划和方案。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">张海河表示县公务员局将积极参与邱湾村塘堰和沟渠整治，力所能及的帮扶一定资金，同时帮助争取兴修水利的项目资金，切实让活动能够取得成效，让群众得到实惠。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/cb7106eeffb08d031fb0e08cdd8c5ba8.jpg\\\\\" /></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县公务员局向邱湾村捐赠三万元现金</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><br />\r\n<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1100','285','李文军','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"1\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日</st1:chsdate>上午，县农业局驻村工作队，在局长邓卫东的带领下，深入潘家湾镇肖家洲村，通过落实沟渠整治方案、整治资金、驻村工作专班，为下一步扎实开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动做好了准备工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">该局工作队通过实地察看肖家洲村蔬菜基地沟渠排灌设施情况，与村干部一起商讨，制定了沟渠整治方案，即主要整治<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>条沟渠，总长度<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18000</span>米，总土方量<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27000</span>方。并当场拿出了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万元资金，用来支持肖家洲村完成蔬菜基地沟渠整治，以确保蔬菜基地排灌畅通、旱涝保收。确立了由副局长熊玉民任组长，从能源办、植保站各抽调两名干部组成工作专班，即日进驻肖家洲村帮助督导实施蔬菜基地沟渠整治。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1101','285','冯浩','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>日下午，陆溪镇召开了三万活动暨农田水利基本建设动员会。县委常委、统战部长李新华，副县长饶自斌出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">李新华指出，万名干部进万村挖万塘，既是一项政治任务，也是一项惠民工程，主题是&ldquo;兴水利、促发展、惠民生&rdquo;，他要求陆溪镇全体干部、各驻村工作队都要积极参与到活动中来，要努力实现党员干部的作风大转变，以饱满的工作热情、良好的精神状态、深厚的群众感情，投入到&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动和农田水利建设中去，要努力实现群众得实惠的目标，要根据各村实际需要，开展水利建设。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">陆溪镇党委书记华红首先传达了省委、省政府动员大会精神，同时要求全镇上下、各级各部门干部必须要提高认识，积极开展好这次的&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，搞好塘堰整治，配合好县直&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队的各项工作开展，确保全镇&ldquo;三万&ldquo;活动和农田水利建设不掉链子，切实将三万活动办成县委满意群众满意的双满意工程。要抓住机遇。努力改善全镇的农业基础设施条件，广大党员干部一定以主人翁意识，将好事办好，实事办事，为群众修一口得实惠的当家塘，让群众看得见，摸得着，真切感受到我们干部为群众带来的实惠，付出的真情，从而赢得群众对我们各项工作的理解支持。要多措并举筹集资金，严格考核，保质保量完成任务，确保这次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动取得圆满成功。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">陆溪镇镇长周素勤主持会议。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1102','285','尹方、税志华','嘉鱼政务网','<p><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>日，鱼岳镇召开&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动动员大会，全面部署安排<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，该镇党委书记李斌提出了&ldquo;四抓&rdquo;要求，即：&ldquo;用真心带真情抓&rdquo;，解生活之需，解干群之困，解生产之要；&ldquo;早谋划带任务抓&rdquo;，精确选址，精细测算，精心施工；&ldquo;求支援带资金抓&rdquo;，争取部门支援，争取社会支援，争取群众支援；&ldquo;出成果带任务抓&rdquo;，确保实效，确保进度，确保任务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">为切实开展好&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，该镇成立了活动领导小组，结合镇情民情制订了活动实施方案，镇直单位和机关干部分别包保到村、到组、到塘堰和沟渠整治工作点。据了解，该镇将集中整治&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>处，沟渠套洗<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>条，切实开展服务&ldquo;水产大镇&rdquo;的相关工作。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1103','285','杨满珍','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日</st1:chsdate>，嘉鱼县总工会党组书记、常务副主席高扬文率该单位驻村工作组一行深入陆溪镇印山村开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">工作组深入印山村各小组，摸查塘堰沟渠隐患，并且为每组的当家塘确定整治方案。工作组还现场拿出三万元修塘资金，以实际行动践行县委县政府&ldquo;挖塘堰、强基础、惠民生&rdquo;的活动。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">高扬文表示，县总工会要以主人翁意识，将好事办好，实事办实，为群众修好当家塘，让群众真切感受到县工会组织为群众带来的实惠。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1104','285','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/f59ee7818e43a89db87e73e3450ef802.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">挖塘现场<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，在嘉鱼县高铁岭镇八斗角村三组的&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;开挖现场，挖掘机正在挥舞着长臂清理淤泥，工人们正在用水泥块将塘壁砌起来，以增强蓄水能力&hellip;&hellip;这是嘉鱼县国土局开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动现场之一。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，高铁岭镇地处丘陵地带，塘堰多淤积，村民历来面临生活用水和生产用水&ldquo;两难&rdquo;境地，干旱时说水贵于油毫不夸张。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为从根本上帮助村民破解用水难题，嘉鱼国土局在推进&ldquo;万民干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动中，结合八斗角等村整村推进农村土地整治示范项目建设，因地制宜开挖塘堰，使村民能有自己的&ldquo;当家塘&rdquo;。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">目前，县国土局已为该村挖塘</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">131</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">口，还有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">17</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">口预计年底前完成。届时将惠及三千余村民，真正实现&ldquo;旱时蓄水，涝时排洪，旱涝保收&rdquo;。<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-09/7b6f7983d5362005fc139cf2cd89e8c4.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1105','285','熊铁山、谢翔、李卓','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">&ldquo;在我们村民眼中，这口塘的用处比天大，政府确实为我们做了一件大好事&rdquo;。朱砂村一位李姓村民边清淤边说道。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"4\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">12</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">晚，官桥镇朱砂村七组当家塘堰施工现场，县经济开发区、县委党校&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队员们干劲十足，正积极清扫路面障碍。消防车彻夜照明，挖掘机、推土机正在紧张的进行着施工，施工队在连夜施工加宽坝面。镇村组干部都加入到了整治工作队伍，周围群众也自发赶来现场帮助清淤。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">历经<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">19</span>个小时紧张施工，凌晨<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>点左右终于在塘堰四周砌起了<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>余米的护坡，预示着初战进展顺利，截至记者发稿时，施工还在进行中。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，自&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动动员大会结束后，县经济开发区和县委党校第一时间赶到朱砂村进行塘堰情况摸底调研，了解到朱砂村当家塘堰始建于七十年代，年久失修，为了急群众之所急，盼群众之所盼，当场确定重点整治朱砂村当家塘堰，全力投入人力物力财力进行升级改造。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据悉，该塘堰改造工程总造价<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">43</span>万元，镇村自筹资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">13</span>万元，争取到县水利局对口支援<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>万元，县经济开发区和县委党校分别支持资金<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>万元和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>万元。经改造后朱砂村七组当家塘堰的蓄水量将达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">45</span>万立方米，灌溉面积可扩大<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">500</span>余亩，受益人口将达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1000</span>余人。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1106','285','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日下午，县长余珂率农办、水利等相关部门负责人一行，赴鱼岳镇十井铺村七组，检查指导该组塘堰整修改造工作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">记者在现场看到，十井铺村七组的这口当家塘堰，由于年久失修，淤塞严重，功能衰退，对附近农田的灌溉效果差，严重影响了村民的生产和生活。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">在向村组干部详细了解了改造和整修塘堰存在的问题和困难后，余珂指出，农田水利建设是影响农业增产、农民增收的命脉工程，水利建设的好坏和群众的切身利益紧密相关。余珂要求在场的相关部门要迅速拿出整修塘堰的方案，根据实际情况，迅速疏通沟渠，修建简易泵站或管道，想方设法改造好这口塘堰，使其发挥应有的灌溉效果。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">针对该组在塘堰整治上存在的资金困难问题，余珂表示，要采取政府财政为主导、社会和农民共同参与的办法，广泛筹措资金。县里在资金上给予一定的帮助，驻村工作队也要给予支持，同时要从农村&ldquo;一事一议&rdquo;中筹措部分资金，并组织义务劳动，广泛发动群众积极参与当家塘堰建设。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">据悉，省委提出开展&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;活动后，我县迅速行动，把它作为今冬明春水利建设的重要平台，抢抓机遇，周密部署，在全县掀起了水利建设高潮。<br />\r\n</font></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1107','285','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\"on\" isrocdate=\"False\" islunardate=\"False\" day=\"3\" month=\"12\" year=\"2011\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日</st1:chsdate>，县委书记熊征宇到洲湾镇调研水利建设和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动开展情况。县委办主任章斌陪同调研。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">熊征宇实地察看了花口村三新垸中心沟渠和后垸泵站，详细了解了洲湾镇水利建设情况和存在的问题。在随后召开的县直单位驻洲湾镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组会议上，熊征宇说，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动和农田水利建设，是加强农业基础设施建设的迫切需要，是抢抓当前水利建设重大政策机遇的迫切需要，务必要高度重视。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">熊征宇指出，各级各部门认识上要再提高，这次三万活动意义非常重大，是联系群众的主渠道，是转变干部作风的大行动，是锻炼干部的好机会，可以真正的帮助老百姓办实事；措施要再强化，要做到三个到位，即领导到位、工作队员到位、群众发动到位；工作要再落实，要迅速落实工作方案，尽快落实帮扶资金，落实开工和竣工的时间；督办要再加强，要督办进度，督办质量，督办作风。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">熊征宇强调，各级各部门要深入宣传、把握重点、抢抓时间，迅速掀起水利建设高潮；要迅速行动，加强督办，把三万活动，水利建设抓紧抓好。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">县驻村工作队汇报了开展&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作以来，各自的工作进展情况和近期打算。牌洲湾镇主要负责人陪同调研。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1108','285','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-04/296fe02c7421080f9278ccf9c2451d1f.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">余珂一行在丰收泵站检查<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">3</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日，县长余珂，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华一行，深入全县重点涵闸、泵站、民垸、湖泊等地，实地察看各地水利设施运行情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">余珂一行先后来到三湖连江进洪闸、马鞍山泵站、余码头泵站、立新泵站、后垸泵站、丰收泵站、河埠险段、耿家湖泵站、金水河、峡港河、东湖围堤、西凉湖围堤、永逸泵站、三乐泵站，现场察看并详细了解各地水利设施运行情况。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在马鞍山排灌站，疯长的水葫芦漂浮聚集在河道上，已严重阻塞了水流，形成安全隐患。针对这一问题，余珂要求该泵站要迅速组织人员，对河道内的水葫芦进行打捞清理，尽快使河道恢复畅通，保障排灌站正常运行。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在洲湾镇各泵站检查时，余珂指出，该镇是水利大镇，一定要抢抓这次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动大兴水利的契机，高标准搞好全镇水利建设；已建好的涵闸和泵站，要派专人进行管理和维护，保证旱能灌，涝能排，随时发挥作用；洲湾的沟渠清淤任务重，要抢抓时间和进度，做好渠坝的硬化，确保一次建好，多年享用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在检查中，余珂要求水利部门一定要把今冬明春农田水利基本建设作为为民谋福祉的一项德政工程，抓紧抓好抓实。要注重实效，切实解决老百姓在生产、生活中遇到的实际困难，同时要把农田水利基本建设同农村环境整治相结合，提高综合整治的效益。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">县政府办主任余忠东、县水利局局长夏毅陪同检查。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 16.3pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1109','285','熊铁山、陈功成 、李卓','中国嘉鱼网','<p><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日，县委书记熊征宇、县长余珂深入官桥镇调研秋冬农田水利建设情况。县委办主任章斌，县政府办主任余忠东，县农办主任耿协刚，县水利局局长夏毅，官桥镇党委书记杨富佳、镇长朱明凤陪同调研。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">熊征宇一行实地查看了官桥镇阴山村湖北大禾现代设施农业，朱砂村七组当家塘堰，官桥村油茶水产基地，大牛山村神塘水库。每到一地，熊征宇、余珂都要详细了解各自的发展情况以及存在的问题。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">在湖北大禾现代设施农业调研时，熊征宇指出，现代农业要发展必须要注重产品品质，培育品牌；要实施精细化管理，提高产品的内在竞争力；要靠管理取得效益，靠品牌开拓市场；要大力发展特色农业，加快发展现代农业，以此推进农业增效，农民增收。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">熊征宇强调，水利建设必须要保障工程质量，要对已有的塘堰护坡加固培厚，重视日常维护管理，利于今后的蓄水灌溉乃至养殖。在建的水利设施必须抢抓时间，保障工程的质量和进度。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">夏毅表示将大力投入技术、专项资金帮助官桥镇开展农田水利建设。杨富佳表示将抢抓&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动机遇，兴水利、促发展、惠民生。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1110','285','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>日上午，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，副县长魏萍一行率县水产局、人防办等部门主要负责人到渡普镇就&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动的开展进行调研。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">熊武华一行实地察看了峡港河淤积情况，深入大路铺村了解新屋鲁塘、担丘塘等拟清淤改造塘堰，并就渡普口村三组危桥改造项目提出了具体意见。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\">在调研过程中，熊武华指出，渡普镇要结合此次&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动，坚持因地制宜，做到早规划早部署，在行动上动真格，下真功；在活动中树典型，带好头；同时还要在项目上突出重点，抢抓进度，做到早动工，开好头，争取在全县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动和新一轮农田水利建设做出表率。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 15.6pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1111','285','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-05/2b27ef7a59d735bdb91e9246a981c9bf.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">挖沟现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一大早，走在田间，冬日的寒意扑面而来。然而在洲湾镇花口村三新垸沟边，扑面而来的是一股股涌动的热潮：飘扬的彩旗，忙碌的身影，挥动的铁锹，轰隆的机器&hellip;&hellip;相互交织，好不热闹。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"5\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">上午，县委书记熊征宇，县委常委、县人武部政委杨长江，及县委办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作组一行</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余人来到驻点村洲湾镇花口村的三新垸沟，与村民一起挥锹铲土，开展清修劳动，为该村修建灌溉沟渠。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">三新垸沟横跨洲湾镇花口村和东岭村，是该村农田灌溉的一条主渠道，总长有</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">800</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">多米，渠道两边</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1300</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亩的蔬菜地都靠它来灌溉。由于年久失修，渠道淤塞严重，长满了杂草，导致水量不大，流动不畅。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;今年上半年这地里种的南瓜就是因为沟里水排不出去，全部都被泡烂了，我们大家早就想清渠，可是没有钱又没有劳力一直没搞。&rdquo;&ldquo;没关系，这次我们三万工作组就是来帮忙的，这沟清好了后，还要进行硬化，以后这地就不怕水淹了。&rdquo;熊征宇一边忙着挖沟一边与身旁的村民王重华交谈道。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊征宇说，别看小小的沟渠，关系到群众生活生产的大问题，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组一定要认真对待，扎实开展工作，利用好冬季兴修水利的好时机，尽快完成各项工程，为明年春耕做好准备工作，让广大群众在</span><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\"> </font><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">&ldquo;万名干部进万村挖万塘&rdquo;中真正得到实惠。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据了解，县委办&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作组此次将拿出</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元的资金，帮助该村将三新垸沟进行清淤并硬化，修建好的沟渠将比之前的增宽</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"1\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">米</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，加深</span><st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\".5\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">0.5</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">米</span></st1:chmetcnv><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，可充分满足周边田地的灌溉需求。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1112','285','鲁攻玉','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">2</font></span><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日，按照县委的统一要求，县人大机关召开治庸问责暨&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作动员大会，对人大机关治庸问责工作和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作进行动员和部署。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">在组织全体机关干部集中学习治庸问责及&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作有关文件和全县动员大会领导讲话精神后，县人大常委会主任李鹏谋对人大机关推进治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作明确提出了四点要求。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">一是不唱空调，真正在思想认识上抓落实。治庸问责工作是当前全县上下组织开展的一项集中整治活动，也是加快建设湖北经济强县、长江临港新城的一次具体现实行动，人大机关全体干部要在思想上高度重视，认识上高度统一，步调上高度一致，努力在治庸问责中改进机关作风，创新工作机制，加强队伍建设，提高干部素质，圆满完成&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作任务，以实际行动为农民群众办实事。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">二是不讲条件，真正在履行职责上抓落实。县人大常委会的工作职责主要就是依法监督、依法决定重大事项。在实际工作中，人大机关全体干部要始终坚持党的领导，坚持寓监督于支持之中，牢固树立&ldquo;不是中心要始终围绕中心，不在一线要始终关注一线&rdquo;观念，对县委决策部署的治庸问责活动以及筹资修路、筹资挖塘等中心工作，人大机关不仅要不讲条件、率先落实，还要履职尽责，加强视察检查督促，真正办成群众满意工程。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">三是不打乱仗，真正在组织实施上抓落实。对于县委统一安排部署的治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动等近期中心工作，办公室要切实制定工作方案，组建工作专班，明确工作职责，认真组织好实施好，不打乱仗。治庸问责工作由人大机关党总支具体负责，突出抓好宣传动员、学习教育、自查反省、深入整改、责任追究、建章立制等重点环节，真正把问题找准、把原因查清，把思想摆正，把体制理顺。&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动由专班人员具体负责，机关干部全员参与，重点是广泛宣传政策，积极出谋划策，帮助联点村完成好改造当家塘、疏通主沟渠等农田水利基本建设任务，增强抗灾减灾能力。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">四是不走过场，真正在增强实效上抓落实。人大机关要以深入开展治庸问责和&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动为契机，进一步加强机关自身建设，健全完善机关各项工作制度、人大代表工作制度以及主任会议、人大常委会议、人民代表大会议事规则，进一步深入基层调查研究，为群众办实事解难事，密切党群干群关系，让组织放心，让群众满意。<br />\r\n</span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1113','285','蔡雪峰','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>日上午，官桥镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动、&ldquo;两违&rdquo;整治、治庸问责活动动员及党报党刊征订工作大会在该镇五楼会议室召开。县&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队全体成员，全体机关干部，镇直各部门负责人，各村（社区）党组织书记、村主任共<span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span>余人参加了会议。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">会议由官桥镇党委副书记、镇长朱明凤主持。该镇党委、政府分管纪检、城建、组织、宣传工作的领导分别传达了相关会议精神，领学了镇党委、政府相关文件，部分镇直部门、村负责人就相关工作作了表态发言。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\">该镇党委书记杨富佳就上述各项工作进行了动员部署与强调，县驻官桥镇&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作队队长、县纪委常委、监察局副局长孙强参加了会议并就&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动提了要求。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1114','285','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\"text-align: center\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/jiayuxianzhiyongwenze/2011-12-09/fc5441d834089cc4f71d117a9943de4e.jpg\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">12</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><font face=\"Times New Roman\">5</font></span><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\">日上午，高铁岭镇召开治庸问责暨&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动动员大会，学习传达县委县政府相关会议精神，并部署全镇治庸问责及&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动工作安排。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">该镇党委书记张行泽指出，在开展治庸问责工作中，要<span style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">树立责任意识，着力解决工作态度、劳动纪律问题；</span>树立勤政意识，着力解决&ldquo;不作为、慢作为、乱作为&rdquo;问题；树立效率意识，着力解决&ldquo;程序不优、能力不强、执行不力&rdquo;问题；树立服务意识，着力解决&ldquo;门难进、脸难看、话难听、事难办&rdquo;问题。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">张行泽指出，&ldquo;三万&rdquo;活动驻村工作组要与各村紧密联系，指导各村对塘堰整治科学规划，合理布局；镇村要积极与工作组对接，积极谋划，主动配合，着重解决与群众关系最密切的突出问题；要积极整合资金、统筹推进，努力建成一批促发展、惠民生的项目。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''\"><font size=\"3\">该镇党委副书记、镇长刘珈对治庸问责、三万活动等当前各项重点工作进行了安排部署。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\"><font size=\"3\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-hansi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-bidi-font-weight: bold\">据悉，高铁岭镇在治庸问责工作中坚持把思想教育、检查整改、树立典型、责任追究、完善机制贯穿始终，突出抓好宣传发动、自查整改、督查问责、总结提高四个环节，采取集中检查、明查暗访、公开承诺、媒体曝光等方式，着力解决机关干部工作中存在的突出问题以及党员干部队伍中存在的能力平庸、业绩平庸，思想懒惰、工作懒惰，纪律作风松散、班子软弱涣散等&ldquo;庸、懒、散、软&rdquo;方面的突出问题。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1115','6','张姝、任建成','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-09/9e7a5fc3fbc25e07b1bfd7177e53bd63.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">报告会现场<br />\r\n</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为深入学习贯彻十七届六中全会精神，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">9</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午，县委中心组召开学习贯彻十七届六中全会精神宣讲报告会。在家的县四大家领导、县委中心组全体成员、各镇党委书记和县直各单位主要负责人参加了学习。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">报告会邀请了市社科联主席王建华宣讲党的十七届六中全会精神。王建华从党的十七届六中全会召开的意义、推进文化改革发展的重要性和紧迫性、中国特色社会主义文化发展道路和文化强国战略目标、推进文化改革发展的主要任务和重大举措等四个方面，对党的十七届六中全会精神进行了深入浅出的解读。整个报告内容丰富、事例翔实，对于进一步把握全会精神实质具有积极的指导意义。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县长余珂在会上讲话，他指出，全县各级各部门要充分认识文化建设的重要性，把文化建设摆在全局工作的重要位置、纳入经济社会发展总体规划；要扎实开展十七届六中全会精神学习宣传活动，并把学习活动与当前的各项工作结合起来，把学习过程变成谋划科学发展、解决突出问题、推动工作的过程；要抓紧制定落实文化强县建设的各项任务措施，进一步深化文化体制改革，加强文化人才队伍建设，为文化大发展大繁荣奠定坚实基础。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">县委副书记李国光主持报告会。他要求广大干部结合各自的工作实际，以这次报告会为契机，牢牢把握全会精神实质，迅速掀起学习宣传十七届六中全会精神的热潮。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1116','6','张旭、谢炜','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日，嘉鱼县召开全县村级团组织换届工作会议，安排部署换届工作，副县长饶自斌出席会议并作重要讲话。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">饶自斌指出，开展村级团组织换届工作，是广大农村青年政治生活中的一件大事，是加强村级团组织建设、发展农村经济、带领青年致富、增强基层团组织战斗力的良好机遇，各镇党委、团委和有关部门要统一思想，充分认识做好村级团组织换届选举工作的重大意义；加强领导和指导，把村级团组织换届工作与抓好当前各项重要工作结合起来，做到统筹兼顾、互相促进，确保高标准、高质量完成村级团组织换届工作任务，为加快建设湖北经济强县，长江临港新城做出新的贡献。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会上，饶自斌强调，在推进村级团组织换届工作过程中，要认真抓好宣传教育，引导青年把注意力从&ldquo;选什么人当官&rdquo;转向&ldquo;选什么人干事&rdquo;上来；坚持严格程序，依法组织选举；坚决杜绝和严肃查处换届选举中的违法违纪行为。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 12pt 0cm; text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 200%; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 12pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">会议宣读了《关于认真做好村级团组织换届工作的通知》及《村级团组织换届选举工作基本程序》。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</span></p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1117','285','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-10/2da351215564c06b256afa64864f609d.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">进行护坡整形</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/zhuantizhuanlan/wanminganbujinwancunwawantang/2011-12-10/11ca9aae42bfa3eabeef04d08dff2bd9.jpg\\\\\" /></o:p></span></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p>帮助村民清理路边垃圾</o:p></span></font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &ldquo;同志们，咱们开工了！&rdquo;</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" day=\\\\\"9\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日下午</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">，在嘉鱼县洲湾镇中堡村五组新建的抗旱沟渠边，随着县委常委、县人武部政委杨长江和县人武部部长王俊一声令下，该部&ldquo;三万&rdquo;工作队的十几名官兵一齐挥起铁锹，开始为渠道进行护坡整形。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 据了解，中堡村是县人武部联点村，当天官兵们进行整形的沟渠是该村<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>组的沙化地灌渠。村委会负责人介绍说，&ldquo;这条渠道是村里新申请的国土整治项目，以前没有这条渠，只能种棉花、小麦，村民收入不高，有了这个灌溉渠就可以改种蔬菜、稻谷了。&rdquo;除了修整渠道，县人武部还拿出<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>万元资金，支持该村维修闸沟泵房、风景渠清淤等水利工程。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 杨长江介绍说：&ldquo;中堡村是<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">98</span>年洲湾大堤倒口的地方，也是很多官兵曾战斗过的地方，人武部官兵要在这里继续发扬抗洪精神，真正帮村民多办实事。&rdquo;</span></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></div>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1118','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2011-12-10/b6f926d572f61b583d304dbdb3b4aa02.jpg\\\\\" /></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">结业仪式现场</span></span></div>\r\n<p><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"9\\\\\" month=\\\\\"12\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2011\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">12</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">，全省乡镇党委书记轮训班在官桥八组结业，省委组织部干部教育处副处长段美峰，咸宁市委常委、组织部长龙良文，嘉鱼县委副书记、县长余珂，嘉鱼县委常委、组织部长袁秋明出席结业典礼。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">段美峰指出，这次培训班主题鲜明，内容丰富，形式灵活，取得了预期的培训效果。他要求学员们回去以后要认真消化所学的知识，认真落实赵斌副省长的重要讲话精神，在思想认识上要切实提高大局意识、忧患意识、争先意识；在科学发展上要创新；在履职能力上加强；在改进作风上有新转变，努力把学习成果转化为自己工作的能力，并应用在今后的工作当中去，更好的为人民群众服务。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">州湾镇党委书记张劲松作为此次培训班的班长，代表全体学员作了讲话。各组分别派出代表就如何做好乡镇党委书记，切实履行好自己的职责谈了自己的认识和感受。</span></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n</span></p>');");
